CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 14, 1960, pg. 2 reads: "Beauty Ignored - Despite the activity of some homeowners to maintain clean properties in upper Francis St. area, there is need for city help to remove this "hokey" pile."
TitMainTitle: Woman holding shovel, standing in front of Insulbrick house with pile of garbage in front of garage, Francis Street, Hill District
